  Featuring a restaurant on site, these cabins are 20 minutes’ drive from Bryce Canyon National Park. All rooms are equipped with free Wi-Fi. Barbecue facilities are provided for guest use.
  
  Each room offers air-conditioning, a satellite TV and coffee-making facilities at Bryce Gatewayinn Cabins. An private bathroom is also provided.
  
  Harold’s Place Restaurant serves breakfast, lunch and dinner daily on site. A 24-hour reception is available to assist guests. Free parking is provided.
  
  Panguitch Lake is 30 minutes’ drive from the cabins. Zion National Park is 65 miles from Harold’s Place Panguitch.
  
  Couples in particular like the location – they rated it **8.1** for a two-person trip.
  
