  ## About this property
  
  ### Tin Roof Cabin at The Cove!
  
  Are you craving a break? This quaint, comfortable cabin is perfect for solo travelers and couples with "Wanna get away vibes". Inside enjoy the charm of stained ceilings, live wood oak, a kitchenette, queen bed, and a beautiful bathroom with a walk in shower. With designated parking and steps away from the restaurant you can enjoy the convenience and comfort. Just 30 minutes to major Florida Springs. Enjoy the real Florida at day and The Cove at night!
  
  The space
  
  This is a true "Tiny Home" vibe approximately 400 sq. feet! Located across from the restaurant. Limit occupancy to 2 guests unless traveling with an infant. Dogs are welcomed however must be approved prior to arrival, including service animals. Dog fee is $50. Please pick up after your pet! Easy access to laundry facility! There is just one queen size bed in this unit. Absolutely no smoking inside!
  
  A charcoal Grill is available upon request. Please let us know in advance if you would like the grill.
  
  Welcome to Airboat Territory. The Cove is the only restaurant on Lake Henderson available by boat. We get plenty of pleasure craft and airboats as customers. Airboats are fun to watch, but can be noisy.
  
  Other things to note
  
  Absolutely no smoking inside the cabin! Cabin is intended for the use of the reserved guest only. Guest staying on the property must be added to the reservation, including dogs. The use of this facility for parties, events or meetings is expressly prohibited unless pre-approved by the facilities manager.
  
  Our prices include all fees. No hidden fees.
  
