  ## About the neighborhood
  
  ### Inverness
  
  Inverness is home to this cabin. The area's natural beauty can be seen at Fort Cooper State Park and Homosassa Springs Wildlife State Park, while Don Garlits Museum of Racing and Circle Square Cultural Center are cultural highlights. Looking to enjoy an event or a game while in town? See what's happening at Citrus County Speedway or Florida Horse Park.
  
