  ## Play.
  
  ![Two people on a via ferrata trail at East Zion Resort, a glaping resort near Zion National Park](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/645527_b45291c000a34a3c8b618d4dd5b55357~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_111,h_74,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/645527_b45291c000a34a3c8b618d4dd5b55357~mv2.jpg)
  
  ### On-Site Activities
  
  At East Zion Resort, you will find a myriad of exciting options for playing and exploring. Take a dip in one of the resort's pools, unwind in one of the hot tubs, engage in friendly matches on the pickleball courts, or for thrill-seekers, East Zion Resort boasts an on-site via ferrata, providing a unique rock-climbing adventure with stunning views.
  
  ​
  
  [LEARN MORE](https://www.eastzionresort.com/resort-amenities)
  
  ### OFF-SITE GUIDED ACTIVITIES
  
  In an exclusive partnership with ROAM Outdoor Adventure Co., Trip Advisor's Best Tour Company in Southern Utah, East Zion Resort offers guided tours of the most iconic areas in and around Zion National Park. This collaboration ensures that visitors can experience the region's natural wonders with expert guidance, making every exploration unforgettable.
  
  [LEARN MORE](https://www.eastzionresort.com/experiences)
  
  ![A person rappelling a slot canyon on a tour recommended by East Zion Resort](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/645527_60fff3506b11451d9aee8668f746d218~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_111,h_74,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/645527_60fff3506b11451d9aee8668f746d218~mv2.jpg)
  
  ## Celebrate.
  
  ![A 3 tiered white and purple cake at a wedding taking place at East Zion Resort, a glamping destination in Orderville, Utah](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/645527_663363a6506d47e493754ba8f5918a48~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_69,h_103,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/645527_663363a6506d47e493754ba8f5918a48~mv2.jpg)
  
  ### Events at East Zion Resort
  
  The resort's beauty extends far beyond unique accommodations. Come, stay, and celebrate your upcoming event or wedding against our stunning red rock cliffs. East Zion Resort offers a private land venue, allowing you to exchange vows or host your event surrounded by Southern Utah's pristine desert landscape. Our customizable packages cater well to both intimate ceremonies and grand celebrations. Choose East Zion Resort for a memorable and stress-free event experience.
  
  [Discover Options](https://www.eastzionresort.com/events)
  
  ![A formal tablescape set for a wedding in Southern Utah at East Zion Resort](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/645527_88b54ca1fd7247eb9d770426782de980~mv2.jpg/v1/fill/w_69,h_103,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/645527_88b54ca1fd7247eb9d770426782de980~mv2.jpg)
  
  ![A glamping yurt At East Zion Resort over looking a valley in Orderville, Utah near Zion National Park](https://static.wixstatic.com/media/cd6661_ce007da7e72a4591af53debf121e0a99~mv2_d_4994_2940_s_4_2.jpg/v1/fill/w_147,h_87,al_c,q_80,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,blur_2,enc_avif,quality_auto/cd6661_ce007da7e72a4591af53debf121e0a99~mv2_d_4994_2940_s_4_2.jpg)
  
  ## A Top-Rated resort
  
  ## Read our Reviews
  
  East Zion Resort stands as one of the highest-rated resorts near Zion National Park with over 900 reviews and a 4.9 star rating on Google earning acclaim for its cleanliness, friendly staff, accommodating service, well-stocked spaces, easy check-in, and of course unique atmosphere. With consistently positive reviews highlighting our commitment to guest satisfaction, the resort has become a trusted choice for those seeking a premium and memorable experience. But don't just take our word for it – discover what others have to say:
  
