  ### **_A Playground_** **of Possibilities**
  
  At Coosawattee River Resort, adventure and relaxation go hand in hand. Dive into one of our three sparkling pools, challenge yourself in our state-of-the-art fitness center, or enjoy a friendly match on our tennis courts. For those who crave the outdoors, our scenic trails are perfect for hiking and biking, offering breathtaking views at every turn. Families will love our parks and playgrounds, where laughter and fun are always in season. Enjoy river activities like fishing, tubing, and swimming in the clear, natural waters of the Coosawattee River.
  
